---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Testimonials from "../../../components/Testimonials";
import GetQuote from "../../../components/buttons/GetQuote.astro";
import ButtonScrollTop from "../../../components/buttons/ButtonScrollTop";
---
<link rel="canonical" href="https://cayadservices.com/for-businesses/auto-auctions" />
<style>
  .custom-background {
    background:
      linear-gradient(hsla(250, 75%, 5%, 0.5), rgba(6, 3, 21, 0.5)),
      url("/img/auction.webp") center center no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
  }
</style>


<Layout title="Auto Auction Shipping | Cayad Autro Transport"
content="We provides reliable transport for vehicles purchased at auctions 10.000+ shippings. 5 stars With a professional team ensuring safe and prompt delivery, call us now ">
  <div
    class="container-fluid flex flex-col items-center justify-center custom-background h-[60vh]"
  >
    <div class="w-[80%]">
      <p
        class="text-white text-[4rem] xs:text-[1.8rem] sm:text-[1.8rem] font-bold"
      >
      Cayad ships vehicles from any auto auction.
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold">
        Nationwide vehicle shipping across the U.S, from any auction.
      </h1>
      <GetQuote />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 flex justify-center mb-8">
    <Testimonials title="Real Auto Transport Testimonials" client:load />
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex justify-between"
    >
      <div class="w-[50%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:mb-8 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
          Fast & Hassle-Free Vehicle Transport
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base mt-8">
          Running an auto auction isn’t just about selling cars—it’s about managing countless moves with precision. A single mistake, miscommunication, or delay can cost you and your clients money. That’s why having a reliable transport partner is essential.
        </p>

        <p class="text-base mt-8">
          At Cayad Auto Transport, we have the technology and network to seamlessly handle inbound and outbound vehicle transport for your auction. Let us take care of the logistics so you can focus on running a successful business.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-[40%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%]">
        <img
          src="/img/auto-auctions2.webp"
          width="1280" height="853"
          class="rounded-xl w-full h-[100%]"
          alt="car shipping from auction"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex flex-col justify-between"
    >
      <h2 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
        Fast & Reliable Vehicle Transport for Any Auction
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base text-[#555] mt-4">
        Cayad Auto Transport moves vehicles for all types of auctions, from large physical events to online marketplaces. Our team ensures smooth and efficient transportation every step of the way
      </p>

      <p class="text-base text-[#555] mt-4">
        We adapt to your processes, following your schedule and regulations to keep everything running on time.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base text-[#555] mt-4">
        With market-driven pricing, we offer competitive rates based on trends and demand. Cayad Auto Transport delivers reliability and efficiency when you need it most.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex justify-between"
    >
      <div class="w-[40%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%]">
        <img src="/img/dealership_circle_3.avif" width="626" height="417" class="rounded-xl" alt="car transport operator inspection"/>
      </div>
      <div class="w-[50%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:mb-8 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
          Expert Single-Unit Vehicle Transport
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base mt-8">
          Cayad Auto Transport handles single-unit moves with speed and precision, whether it’s a short trip or over 140 miles away.<br>
          Our scalable capacity ensures fast response times and skilled vehicle handling for one car or a hundred.<br>
          With industry-leading transit times, we move vehicles faster and more efficiently than the competition.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex justify-between"
    >
      <div class="w-[50%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:mb-8 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
          Nationwide Pickup & Delivery
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base mt-8">
          With over 15,000 vetted carriers across the country, we ensure reliable vehicle transport from coast to coast.<br>
          All carriers meet strict insurance and safety standards and understand the security protocols required in the auction industry.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-[40%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%]">
        <img src="/img/dealership_circle_5.webp" width="435" height="266" class="rounded-xl" alt="auto transport from dealership usa map 2"/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  

  <div class="flex flex-col xs:flex-col sm:flex-col items-center h-max w-full">
    <div class="w-[80%] xs:w-[100%] sm:w-[100%] xs:p-4 sm:p-4">
      <h2
        data-aos="fade-up"
        class="text-[2.5rem] xs:text-xl text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold"
      >
      The Ideal Auto Transport Partner for Dealerships
      </h2>

      <div
        class="grid mt-8 grid-cols-2 xs:grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 w-full gap-6"
      >
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.3s"
        >
          <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold">
            Experience
          </h5>
          <p class="py-4">
            Cayad Auto Transport specializes in safe and efficient vehicle moves. Last year, we handled over 10,000 shipments, including weekend deliveries.<br>
            Trust us for your local or long-distance vehicle transportation needs.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.5s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold">
              Technology
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4">
              We use the latest technology to make car shipping easier and more convenient for our customers.<br>
              Our innovative solutions and exceptional service help drive progress in your operations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.7s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 py-4 text-xl text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold">
              Innovation
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4"  >
              We prioritize product and service innovations to drive our customers' success.<br>
              As experts in market analysis, we ensure you get the best rates available.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          data-aos="fade-up"
          class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-btn-blue duration-300 wow fadeInUp"
          data-wow-delay="0.9s"
        >
          <div class="team-item p-4 xs:p-0 sm:p-0">
            <h5 class="mb-2 text-xl py-4 text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold">
              Responsiveness
            </h5>
            <p class="py-4"  >
              With a network of over 15,000 carriers and a team of experienced transportation and customer service experts, Cayad Auto Transport has the capacity and expertise to meet your needs quickly and efficiently.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full mt-12 mb-12 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:w-full sm:w-full xs:flex-col sm:flex-col xs:px-4 sm:px-4 flex flex-col justify-between"
    >
      <h2 class="text-[#19171fd2] font-semibold text-[2.5rem]">
        How Cayad Can Help Your Auction Business
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base text-[#555] mt-4">
        <span class="text-[#555] font-bold">End-to-end solutions:</span>
        Cayad collaborates with your team to enhance service and transparency. We benchmark our costs and capabilities against your current providers to prove our value.
      </p>

      <p class="text-base text-[#555] mt-4">
        <span class="text-[#555] font-bold">Preferred transporter:</span>
        Cayad delivers top-tier service, handling cars, trucks, motorcycles, and more. With the right equipment, we simplify transport for luxury, collector, and inoperable vehicles.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base text-[#555] mt-4">
        <span class="text-[#555] font-bold">Augment established carriers:</span>
        Cayad extends your local carriers' reach with our nationwide network, ensuring smooth long-distance moves and greater efficiency in your operations.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="w-full flex mb-8 flex-col items-center xs:min-w-[100%] xs:px-0 sm:min-w-[100%] sm:px-0 mx-auto overflow-hidden px-0"
  >
    <div
      class="w-[80%] xs:min-w-[100%] xs:px-4 sm:min-w-[100%] sm:px-4 py-10 px-0"
    >
      <h2 class="text-4xl text-[#19171fd2] font-medium mb-10">
        Why Choose Cayad Auto Transport for Auto Auction Shipping?
      </h2>
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 xs:grid-cols-1 gap-10"
      >
        <div class="wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <img src="/img/dollar.webp" width="1080" height="1080" class="w-24 h-20 mb-2" alt="auto transport from auction dollar logo"/>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">Competitive Prices</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                At Cayad Auto Transport, we offer top-quality service at affordable rates. Our transparent pricing ensures great value without hidden fees or compromising quality.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <img src="/img/easy.webp" width="1080" height="1080" class="w-24 h-20 mb-2" alt="car transport from auction easy logo"/>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">Ease of shipping</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                We make vehicle transport hassle-free, handling every detail from pickup to delivery. Our trained staff ensures a smooth, efficient process for your peace of mind.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex mb-10 wow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
            <img src="/img/call.webp" width="1080" height="1080" class="w-24 h-20 mb-2" alt="auto shipping from auctions call logo"/>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h5 class="font-semibold">Personalized assistance</h5>
              <p class="xs:text-start sm:text-start mb-0">
                Every shipment is unique, and our experts provide personalized support at every step. Whether you need updates or have questions, we’re here to help. Your satisfaction is our priority.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-[95%] wow"
          data-aos="fade-right"
          data-aos-delay="100"
          style="min-height: 400px;"
        >
          <div class="h-full">
            <img
              src="/img/auction.webp"
              width="1224" height="682"
              class="object-cover rounded-xl w-full h-full"
              alt="auto auction transport"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <ButtonScrollTop client:load />
</Layout>